txt.en: 'Well done. Well done, indeed! You've proven yourself a skilled hunter. I dare say you've still got room for improvement, though.'
Duilin, and avid hunter, has wagered a bet that you cannot bag as many game as he can!
Beasts can be found throughout Southern Ithilien.\n\nYou should defeat beasts in Southern Ithilien.
Duilin is located in Bâr Húrin.\n\nYou should talk to Duilin.

'Derufin and I are avid hunters. We honed our skills in the Blackroot Vale during our youth, you see. How about a small wager, all in good sport? I bet you can't bag a dozen beasts before you need to be on your way!'
